Generate Plate Seeds
We pick 4–7 random plate centers across the map.
Each plate gets:
an ID
a motion vector (dx, dy)
a type (continental or oceanic)
a color (for debugging)

Assign Each Hex to a Plate
Compute Plate Boundaries
Apply Tectonic Effects to Elevation


